spec_data.Name: perl-Test-Exit
spec_data.Description:
Test::Exit Perl module provides some simple tools for testing code that might
call exit(), providing you with the status code without exiting the test file.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Mon 14 Aug 2017 08:48:39 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Test that some code calls exit without terminating testing
